CleanTGIFormat(string)

Returns a string of the TGI in the same format as ToString() for comparison.

public static string CleanTGIFormat(string tgi)

Parameters

tgi string

TGI string to parse

Returns

string

The TGI properly formated delimited by comma space, in the format of 0x########, 0x########, 0x########, with leading zeros added up to 8 characters each.

Remarks

The input string must contain three hexadecimal numbers, each prefixed with 0x.
